Miłosna  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Godkowo, within Elbląg County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  west of Godkowo,  east of Elbląg, and  north-west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
